<D>__{no. i take it you don't either?}
<P>__{(as lila shakes her head)}
<D>__{how long?}
<C>__{lila}
<D>__{last friday. she left work, and home... i was in tucson over the weekend... i haven't heard from her, not even a phone call.}
<C>__{sam}
<D>__{and you thought she'd come up here, to me? if she had, what reason would she have for not calling you?}
<C>__{lila}
<D>__{a good reason, i suppose.}
<C>__{sam}
<P>__{(slightly exasperated)}
<D>__{well what do you think, we eloped or something? or we're living in sin and...}
<C>__{lila}
<D>__{mr. loomis, you're so busy being defensive that you haven't even reacted to the most serious fact of all. mary is missing.}
<C>__{sam}
<D>__{i was getting to that!}
<C>__{lila}
<D>__{what do you know about it?}
