<D>__{nothing! you're putting me on the defensive.}
<C>__{lila}
<D>__{look, if you two are in this thing together, i don't care, it's none of my business... but i want to see mary. i want her to tell me she's all right and it's none of my business. then i will go back to phoenix and...}
<A>__{she stops, the anxiety and fear building up in her, her eyes beginning to fill with worried tears. sam studies her for a moment, then turns and calls:}
