<P>__{(seriously)}
<D>__{never mind my ego. let's talk about mary.}
<A>__{their attention is distracted by a man who has strolled quietly into the room. he ignores them, walks past them, goes behind the counter, takes down a sign reading "closed for lunch," walks back to the door, closes door, hangs the sign across the door window, locks the door, turns to sam and lila, folds his arms, smiles a particularly unfriendly smile.}
<C>__{arbogast}
